event VesterAdded(address vester, string vestingType, uint256 amount)
event VestingTypeAdded(string type_, uint256 initialRelease, uint256 releaseRate, uint256 totalLockTime, uint256 claimPeriod, uint256 numberOfClaims, uint256 initialCooldown)
function addVester(address vester, string vesting, uint256 amount) returns (bool)
function addVestingType(string type_, uint256 initialRelease, uint256 releaseRate, uint256 totalLockTime, uint256 claimPeriod, uint256 numberOfClaims_, uint256 initialCooldown) returns (bool)
